# Title: CreateRemoteThread API and LoadLibrary
# Author: Roberto Rodriguez @Cyb3rWard0g
# Date: 2019-08-11
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential use of CreateRemoteThread api and LoadLibrary function to inject DLL into a process
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1055.001, detection.threat-hunting
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-threat-hunting/windows/create_remote_thread/create_remote_thread_win_loadlibrary.yml

StartFunction="LoadLibraryA" StartModule="*\\kernel32.dll"